    "description": "<i>A strange visitor in a family. <br>Since they've come, none of them can continue living as they did. <br>Who was that visitor? <br>Could they be divine?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A strange visitor.</h2>In DIVINITY, you play as a strange visitor in a family. Your mysterious appearance has ignited desires in each of the family members. With your divine gifts, you can help them to achieve their desires and reach divinity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/9488eb7c03f5c90735c657449185f6d5.avif?t=1668912962\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infatuate family members.</h2>Spend time with family members as they engage in activities throughout the estate, and see how they display their feelings towards you. Day &amp; night cycles, randomized events and guests keep the estate interesting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Divine sight.</h2>Use your divine sight to find the most infatuated family member. This will also show how close you are to revealing their desires.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/8195ad7a51693ecb5af915a37be11099.poster.avif?t=1668912962\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/8195ad7a51693ecb5af915a37be11099.webm?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/8195ad7a51693ecb5af915a37be11099.mp4?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manipulate time.</h2>Use your powers to speed up time and see how their infatuation with you changes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/55f8aecb1e1585c034bf1fc5262113f9.poster.avif?t=1668912962\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/55f8aecb1e1585c034bf1fc5262113f9.webm?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/55f8aecb1e1585c034bf1fc5262113f9.mp4?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fulfil their desires.</h2>Each family member has a desire, which is a puzzle that you must successfully solve for them to be a step closer to reaching divinity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/e7e4cae268549fd8f8ecfc291a3dc351.poster.avif?t=1668912962\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/e7e4cae268549fd8f8ecfc291a3dc351.webm?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/e7e4cae268549fd8f8ecfc291a3dc351.mp4?t=1668912962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>This game is based upon the 1968 film Theorem</i><br>",
